website_summaries.verdict: With a whopping 275 pieces, you're sure to find something you like here. Just be aware that the colors they send may not be the colors you expect.
pros: 275-piece tackle set that includes frog lures, hard, soft, and metal lures, poppers, minnows, and accessories such as swivels and hooks
Comes in a plastic tackle box
cons: The colors they send are random, so you won't necessarily get what you see in the product pictures
The hooks included here are very small
